SERVERLESS ONLY — no EC2, Docker, ECS, EKS, containers, or traditional servers.

ALLOWED AWS SERVICES:
  Lambda, API Gateway, Aurora Serverless v2, S3, CloudFront,
  DynamoDB, Cognito, Step Functions, Secrets Manager, SSM Parameter Store

FORBIDDEN:
  EC2, ECS, EKS, Fargate, Elastic Beanstalk, Docker, containers of any kind,
  self-managed web servers, VMs

DEPLOYMENT:
  AWS SAM (template.yaml) only.
  One CloudFormation stack per environment: amaradata-prod, amaradata-staging.

SCALING:
  Lambda auto-scales. Pay-per-use. No pre-provisioned capacity.

SECRETS:
  All credentials in AWS Secrets Manager at /<tenant>/<env>/<name>.
  Never hardcode credentials. Never commit .env files.
